<body>
    <h1>Task 13 - Technical Document</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"9f2ea2a50683" id=3D"Task13-TechnicalDocument-1.Introduction=
">1. Introduction</h1>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"e293b02c4b26" id=3D"Task13-TechnicalDocument-1.1Purpose">1.=
1 Purpose</h1>
<p local-id=3D"e159f6173287">The purpose of this technical document is to d=
escribe the <strong>design, implementation, and operational details</strong=
> of an automated observability stack deployed on <strong>Amazon Web Servic=
es (AWS)</strong> using a Linux shell script.</p>
<p local-id=3D"d1440cdf222f">The observability stack consists of the follow=
ing open-source tools:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"c4a7b3a29481"><strong>Grafana</strong> =E2=80=93 Visualizati=
on and monitoring dashboards</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"c87dfa997c90"><strong>Prometheus</strong> =E2=80=93 Metrics =
collection and monitoring engine</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"e57adf2d3bc0"><strong>Loki</strong> =E2=80=93 Log aggregatio=
n and storage system</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"181ee160e1ac"><strong>Mimir</strong> =E2=80=93 Long-term met=
rics storage backend</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"d287bc140ce9"><strong>Promtail</strong> =E2=80=93 Log collec=
tion agent that forwards logs to Loki</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"b6f0f179c2da">This document provides a comprehensive overvie=
w of:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"e5df4165dbbd">Infrastructure setup</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"bf4463e56ba3">System architecture</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"1a765bfb4d20">Automation processes</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"0f93cc38c504">Monitoring implementation</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"e98e4d3fc0c1">Deployment and operational procedures</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"efcf721ef9d5">Alignment with AWS Well-Architected Framework =
principles</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"91ec6dca4ef8">The document is intended for multiple stakehol=
ders involved in the design, implementation, and operation of the solution.=
</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"6d4783b9-7251-4e2f-b2e6-06e=
283d2eddf" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"51750537ad50">Stakeholder</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"5b28cfb716bf">Purpose</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"cb583802193b"><strong>CTO</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"4ad78b3be6d6">Understand the monitoring strategy and operati=
onal visibility capabilities of the system</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a8a738914518"><strong>Developers</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a2ee48fd8118">Understand how logs and metrics are collected =
and visualized</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"9f47e81f7195"><strong>Solution Architects</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c638aab39310">Evaluate the system architecture and infrastru=
cture design</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a7d8d8363eff"><strong>DevOps Engineers</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e242b8204542">Maintain, extend, and operate the monitoring s=
tack</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"0b6634d99d37"><strong>Resellers / Technical Partners</strong=
></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7cb07b6797d6">Demonstrate the architecture and value of the =
observability solution to customers</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"dfa1bc79f6d2" id=3D"Task13-TechnicalDocument-1.2Scope">1.2 =
Scope</h1>
<p local-id=3D"54b9fb1df8b4">This document focuses on the <strong>automated=
 deployment and configuration of an observability stack on an AWS EC2 insta=
nce using a Linux shell script</strong>.</p>
<p local-id=3D"b77cde993e09">The scope includes:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"3397ec6d8c26">Infrastructure preparation on AWS</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"e03b79986239">Installation and configuration of monitoring t=
ools</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"05c2118f2758">Service initialization and automation</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"917478ffb493">Basic monitoring and logging configuration</p>=
</li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"c76f3052cb83">Verification and validation of system function=
ality</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"4a41dc65447b">The scope <strong>does not include the followi=
ng items</strong>, as they are outside the assignment requirements:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"da690830b742">Infrastructure provisioning using Infrastructu=
re-as-Code tools such as Terraform or CloudFormation</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"4f5bc10a41a4">Enterprise-grade high availability monitoring =
clusters</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"eb4b1c772796">Multi-region deployment strategies</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"64cb158870c9">Production-grade security mechanisms such as T=
LS termination and authentication providers</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"c42f97bed0ed">Full CI/CD pipelines for application deploymen=
ts</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"be36ca2b1105">The implementation is intended to demonstrate =
<strong>basic observability automation practices</strong> suitable for lear=
ning environments, demonstrations, or small-scale deployments.</p>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"e346d5c348b5" id=3D"Task13-TechnicalDocument-2.OverviewofDe=
vOpsProject">2. Overview of DevOps Project</h1>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"15e8ecb56d19" id=3D"Task13-TechnicalDocument-2.1Definition"=
>2.1 Definition</h1>
<p local-id=3D"5d3a606d2be9">DevOps is a modern software engineering practi=
ce that combines <strong>development (Dev)</strong> and <strong>operations =
(Ops)</strong> teams to improve collaboration, automation, and delivery eff=
iciency.</p>
<p local-id=3D"82aadb4d8260">The primary goals of DevOps include:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"1b4c5615c097">Automating infrastructure and deployments</p><=
/li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"7251550611dd">Improving monitoring and operational visibilit=
y</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"aaa405f41aec">Increasing software delivery speed</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"985897b0809d">Reducing system downtime</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"d459f324dc38">Enabling faster incident detection and resolut=
ion</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"c43957045e9f">In this project, DevOps principles are applied=
 to <strong>automate the deployment of a monitoring and observability infra=
structure</strong>.</p>
<p local-id=3D"20093e23fc5d">The observability stack provides capabilities =
such as:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"bcc17505e4b7">Collecting infrastructure and service metrics<=
/p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"f5644594489a">Aggregating application and system logs</p></l=
i>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"c2fcd34bbd45">Visualizing operational data through dashboard=
s</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"d090915d69e8">Providing insights into system health and perf=
ormance</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"5c8c147f0dca">By automating the deployment process through s=
cripting, the solution enables <strong>consistent, repeatable, and reliable=
 infrastructure setup</strong>.</p>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"e29a96f3d5ba" id=3D"Task13-TechnicalDocument-2.2KeyPrincipl=
es">2.2 Key Principles</h1>
<p local-id=3D"493fe3fa66d2">This implementation aligns with the <strong>AW=
S Well-Architected Framework</strong>, which consists of six pillars that g=
uide cloud architecture best practices.</p>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"e21a2b306538" id=3D"Task13-TechnicalDocument-OperationalExc=
ellence">Operational Excellence</h2>
<p local-id=3D"ef9ff7894423">Operational excellence focuses on <strong>auto=
mation, operational visibility, and continuous improvement</strong>.</p>
<p local-id=3D"bc1c69164149">Implementation in this project includes:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"f10e760181aa">Automated infrastructure configuration using a=
 <strong>single deployment script</strong></p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"5493b663226d">Automated installation of monitoring services<=
/p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"4ec2d7b8ed6f">Centralized monitoring dashboards using Grafan=
a</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"b0b3c194b2a5">System service management using <strong>system=
d</strong></p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"548a475e4b39">These practices improve operational efficiency=
 and reduce manual intervention.</p>
<p local-id=3D"c7b16d0d7180"><strong>Not implemented (out of scope):</stron=
g></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"8677df44ef2f">Infrastructure automation using Terraform or C=
loudFormation</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"3a479b16094c">Automated rollback mechanisms</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"0bae3a75edd6" id=3D"Task13-TechnicalDocument-Security">Secu=
rity</h2>
<p local-id=3D"64eba5645f4b">The security pillar focuses on protecting syst=
ems and data through <strong>access control, isolation, and secure configur=
ation</strong>.</p>
<p local-id=3D"0931b3cd9681">Security practices implemented in this solutio=
n include:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"fad425796bf8">Dedicated service users for monitoring service=
s</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"0618b385a0a1">Running services with <strong>non-root privile=
ges</strong></p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"848518d33e7f">Limiting network exposure through <strong>AWS =
Security Groups</strong></p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"500507a900c7">Required ports exposed:</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"1dbd2270-11a2-464d-aabd-717=
a892f868c" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"b0e5ede8cb55">Service</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"1927cd2905bc">Port</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"acc2fb4553e0">Purpose</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"fc99d998b103">Grafana</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3363c8790f33">3000</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f3dc7b7388e5">Dashboard access</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"609790369ae0">Prometheus</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ccf96fd1aa82">9090</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"4365a33f7202">Metrics interface</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5a0448069568">Loki</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"19836a94aebb">3100</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a8d4e01fd1a3">Log ingestion</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"617214d08c87">Mimir</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7588daa3f6ee">9009</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"db47c14b79b6">Metrics storage API</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"e39de5b94c5d"><strong>Security mechanisms not implemented du=
e to scope limitations:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"b0bc1a2c3a65">TLS/HTTPS encryption</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"e2b7ca329215">Identity and Access Management (IAM) integrati=
on</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"ee321979f6ce">OAuth authentication for Grafana</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"4c89f96e4886">These enhancements would be required for produ=
ction environments.</p>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"94aa82c45d8a" id=3D"Task13-TechnicalDocument-Reliability">R=
eliability</h2>
<p local-id=3D"b2d4a15106ce">Reliability ensures systems can <strong>recove=
r from failures and maintain service continuity</strong>.</p>
<p local-id=3D"e6384c242859">Reliability features implemented:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"d432050fb007">Services configured with <strong>systemd resta=
rt policies</strong></p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"6661e1cd99fa">Services automatically restart on failure</p><=
/li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"a846a7b8b92f">Services enabled to start automatically after =
system reboot</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"ba05e0cb27f4">Limitations:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"3097a28f68ce">Single EC2 instance deployment</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"f322755536ea">No load balancing</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"c12b8a49a0e5">No high availability configuration</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"3e5b6a5eca94">For production environments, reliability impro=
vements would include <strong>multi-AZ deployments and redundancy mechanism=
s</strong>.</p>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"4e6184a37b3d" id=3D"Task13-TechnicalDocument-PerformanceEff=
iciency">Performance Efficiency</h2>
<p local-id=3D"083c5af7bcfe">Performance efficiency ensures optimal utiliza=
tion of computing resources.</p>
<p local-id=3D"65964614fd9d">In this project:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"3a928cfcad3f">Lightweight monitoring tools were selected</p>=
</li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"95dc57666006">Local storage is used for metrics and logs</p>=
</li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"cc5f189e8dac">Monitoring services run on a single EC2 instan=
ce</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"538df90a6397">This configuration is sufficient for <strong>l=
ow to moderate monitoring workloads</strong>.</p>
<p local-id=3D"4af417aee238">Future improvements could include:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"40772bdb00f1">Distributed monitoring clusters</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"9cad3303260a">Object storage integration such as Amazon S3</=
p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"28f55772216a">Horizontal scaling of monitoring services</p><=
/li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"d8c71d2aed11" id=3D"Task13-TechnicalDocument-CostOptimizati=
on">Cost Optimization</h2>
<p local-id=3D"a9617ba2d029">Cost optimization focuses on minimizing unnece=
ssary infrastructure expenses.</p>
<p local-id=3D"d5d258149a05">This solution achieves cost efficiency through=
:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"30e5e2b63793">Use of open-source monitoring tools</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"f3cb31d0a1d9">Deployment on a single EC2 instance</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"4e72ae215bab">Avoidance of additional managed monitoring ser=
vices</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"6c0894f5bee2">Recommended instance type:</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">t2.medi=
um</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"b0be162ea761">This instance size provides sufficient resourc=
es while maintaining low operational costs.</p>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"f53dac4b93bd" id=3D"Task13-TechnicalDocument-Sustainability=
">Sustainability</h2>
<p local-id=3D"2152b08cf8dc">The sustainability pillar focuses on minimizin=
g environmental impact through efficient resource usage.</p>
<p local-id=3D"9a8acef99b32">This deployment contributes to sustainability =
by:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"66338d708e8a">Using minimal infrastructure resources</p></li=
>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"a317d81540fe">Consolidating monitoring tools on a single hos=
t</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"af9e71dde74c">Using efficient open-source monitoring technol=
ogies</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"50adcd2cc6eb">Future improvements could include:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"efde0bcd9c61">Automatic scaling</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"c4a82f8750c9">Resource optimization strategies</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"3b7b47c15083" id=3D"Task13-TechnicalDocument-2.3GoalsandObj=
ectives">2.3 Goals and Objectives</h1>
<p local-id=3D"242ec968a836">The key objectives of this DevOps implementati=
on are:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"fcc443dccd0a">Automate the deployment of an observability st=
ack</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"b04b0a6c64d9">Enable centralized monitoring and logging</p><=
/li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"b541bbc1f46b">Provide operational dashboards for system visi=
bility</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"fd519724b792">Reduce manual configuration effort</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"f664353ac899">Ensure reproducible monitoring environments</p=
></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"a8c82a692172" id=3D"Task13-TechnicalDocument-2.4Constraints=
andAssumptions">2.4 Constraints and Assumptions</h1>
<h3 local-id=3D"c2a2f6c73fe8" id=3D"Task13-TechnicalDocument-Constraints">C=
onstraints</h3>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"937ee342-9887-4c77-82c0-a81=
7352a2fe4" class=3D"confluenceTable">
