<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7affef76860f">No paid monitoring tools used</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<h3 local-id=3D"70af525e1ad6" id=3D"Task13-TechnicalDocument-Assumptions">A=
ssumptions</h3>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"0859398fe10d">An EC2 instance is already provisioned</p></li=
>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"929d84d19405">Ubuntu operating system is installed</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"4fab65902680">Security group rules allow access to required =
ports</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"6e7637a48561">Internet connectivity is available</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"a71f8942e382" id=3D"Task13-TechnicalDocument-3.Architecture=
andInfrastructure">3. Architecture and Infrastructure</h1>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"58e989b2b421" id=3D"Task13-TechnicalDocument-3.1Infrastruct=
ureOverview">3.1 Infrastructure Overview</h1>
<p local-id=3D"dc575b7cb980">The monitoring stack is deployed within <stron=
g>AWS Cloud infrastructure</strong>.</p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-=
file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img cla=
ss=3D"confluence-embedded-image image-center" alt=3D"diagram-export-3-16-20=
26-12_36_35-PM-20260316-070657.png" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"7=
642507bcdba6d5c9b1a351f128218b16d3e78d0e8e2aabb28c739e7c6835355" data-image=
-src=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1864237106/d=
iagram-export-3-16-2026-12_36_35-PM-20260316-070657.png?version=3D1&amp;mod=
ificationDate=3D1773644837354&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-heigh=
t=3D"1024" data-width=3D"2111" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-lin=
ked-resource-id=3D"1863418053" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-link=
ed-resource-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"diagr=
am-export-3-16-2026-12_36_35-PM-20260316-070657.png" data-base-url=3D"https=
://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resource-content-type=3D"image/pn=
g" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"1864237106" data-linked-resource-co=
ntainer-version=3D"2" data-media-id=3D"5c1f6c91-580e-4ac7-85d6-b95567f9f240=
" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"227"></span>
<p local-id=3D"e3bca078c82a"></p>
<p local-id=3D"dc8407ce5c66">The architecture includes:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"ef4e6b057300">AWS Virtual Private Cloud (VPC)</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"c77969943669">Public Subnet</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"a412c627f270">EC2 instance hosting monitoring services</p></=
li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"10bb49033cb4">All observability services run on the EC2 inst=
ance.</p>
<p local-id=3D"be76a6dbd643">Components deployed:</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"a095875b-a015-46fc-bb78-251=
aaaf86d17" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"71878490f1dd">Component</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"748810df4300">Role</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"49c945a1532c">Prometheus</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"432a4ab221b3">Metrics collection</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8dd058a2f797">Loki</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"40879cf15e28">Log storage</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"328c74780e17">Mimir</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"486451b7adea">Metrics storage backend</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"306a14831343">Promtail</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"35bfcaf92ee9">Log collector</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2d603552e950">Grafana</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f720a0fb0e4f">Visualization dashboards</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"54d4d0c0ed8d" id=3D"Task13-TechnicalDocument-3.2Environment=
s">3.2 Environments</h1>
<p local-id=3D"564e95fb06b2">Enterprise DevOps workflows typically involve =
multiple environments.</p>
<p local-id=3D"965566335962">Common environments include:</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"512908ad-c0cf-46e4-9333-61f=
3ed610e81" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"be00c3c32a81">Environment</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"ccd719228225">Purpose</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"0a336075ae9a">Development</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7101e744afda">Application development</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6228a3f05e3a">Testing</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e407749d1d0e">Functional validation</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"848648964528">Staging</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"02c888aed174">Pre-production testing</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"1117d4909690">Production</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"fdf27674231c">Live deployment</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"a5e67b56d93c"><strong>For this assignment:</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"e325c4900ab6">Only a <strong>single environment is implement=
ed</strong>.</p>
<p local-id=3D"cf60364e2471">Reason:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"30d16d6c00ee">Project scope limited to monitoring stack depl=
oyment</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"e5f1af749ef1">No application deployment workflow involved</p=
></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"d939cdfd8ae2" id=3D"Task13-TechnicalDocument-3.4Application=
Architecture&amp;UserRequestFlow">3.4 Application Architecture &amp; User R=
equest Flow</h1>
<p local-id=3D"1700c6d7fe28">The monitoring architecture supports the follo=
wing flows.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"3312d87a1de9" id=3D"Task13-TechnicalDocument-MetricsFlow">M=
etrics Flow</h3>
<p local-id=3D"0a30f033efe7">Prometheus collects metrics and sends them to =
Mimir for storage.</p>
<p local-id=3D"d0ea129b249a">Grafana queries both Prometheus and Mimir to v=
isualize metrics.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"8aa3e4d7e72e" id=3D"Task13-TechnicalDocument-LogFlow">Log F=
low</h3>
<p local-id=3D"38944f279104">System logs are collected by Promtail and forw=
arded to Loki.</p>
<p local-id=3D"ccd698e866bf">Grafana queries Loki to visualize log data.</p=
>
<h3 local-id=3D"9f2eaeba8d0e" id=3D"Task13-TechnicalDocument-UserAccessFlow=
">User Access Flow</h3>
<p local-id=3D"7ed9847cdba8">Users access the Grafana dashboard via a web b=
rowser to view metrics and logs.</p>
<hr>
