<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"221acbf25a65" id=3D"Task13-TechnicalDocument-4.DevelopmentP=
ractices">4. Development Practices</h1>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"69ec9b205e12" id=3D"Task13-TechnicalDocument-4.1VersionCont=
rol">4.1 Version Control</h1>
<p local-id=3D"89890a84dafe">Version control practices are <strong>not impl=
emented in this assignment</strong>.</p>
<p local-id=3D"3186922df5a8">Recommended best practice:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"32eb1c93b5e1">Store deployment scripts in a <strong>Git repo=
sitory</strong></p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"687be38165a2">Use branching strategies for development</p></=
li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"9dc9d4f92634">Perform peer code reviews</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"6612d80513d4" id=3D"Task13-TechnicalDocument-4.2ContinuousI=
ntegration">4.2 Continuous Integration</h1>
<p local-id=3D"436a197a181c">Continuous Integration (CI) is <strong>not app=
licable in this implementation</strong>.</p>
<p local-id=3D"8a3aa150ef43">Reason:</p>
<p local-id=3D"ff9007cd03f3">The project focuses on <strong>infrastructure =
deployment automation rather than application development pipelines</strong=
>.</p>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"3c26c1fcfa34" id=3D"Task13-TechnicalDocument-4.3AutomatedTe=
sting">4.3 Automated Testing</h1>
<p local-id=3D"b2cb23db166f">Automated testing frameworks were <strong>not =
implemented</strong>.</p>
<p local-id=3D"cf8085f7614e">Possible future improvements include:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"1fef2fd67226">Script validation testing</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"6b27902f69bd">Infrastructure health checks</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"fab12fa91e74" id=3D"Task13-TechnicalDocument-4.4CodeQuality=
andAnalysis">4.4 Code Quality and Analysis</h1>
<p local-id=3D"793df972e2d6">Static code analysis tools were <strong>not im=
plemented due to project scope</strong>.</p>
<p local-id=3D"3ab4055dda84">Future improvements could include:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"c4b70f93edec">ShellCheck for script validation</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"951777e562c9">automated linting pipelines</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"8a9280acd9b2" id=3D"Task13-TechnicalDocument-5.Deploymentan=
dReleaseManagement">5. Deployment and Release Management</h1>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"5e7ec24dd91e" id=3D"Task13-TechnicalDocument-5.1DeploymentS=
trategy">5.1 Deployment Strategy</h1>
<p local-id=3D"6e11488670e1">The deployment strategy uses a <strong>script-=
based automated deployment model</strong>.</p>
<p local-id=3D"a78ce603b08c">Execution command:</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">sudo ba=
sh deploy.sh</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"95e27c8ad606">Deployment process includes:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p local-id=3D"c8be2098ee02">Installing system dependencies</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"48d67f75eef9">Downloading monitoring binaries</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"fcc777d6fa24">Creating service users</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"543bca49cece">Generating configuration files</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"bb506e9d09c2">Starting system services</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"3ef822204fe3">Enabling services for automatic startup</p></l=
i>
</ol>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"e64c0eb54e97" id=3D"Task13-TechnicalDocument-5.2Configurati=
onManagement">5.2 Configuration Management</h1>
<p local-id=3D"509ad93b3898">Configuration management is implemented throug=
h:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"dd3700d39053">YAML configuration files</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"be8267c02d04">shell script automation</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"0387719868e4">Configuration files include:</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">prometh=
eus.yml
loki-config.yaml
mimir-config.yaml
grafana datasource configuration</pre>
</div>
</div>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"ab5ed3fd0dbf" id=3D"Task13-TechnicalDocument-5.3ContinuousD=
elivery/Deployment">5.3 Continuous Delivery / Deployment</h1>
<p local-id=3D"771251a054c2">Continuous Delivery pipelines are <strong>not =
implemented</strong>.</p>
<p local-id=3D"a719beed949d">Reason:</p>
<p local-id=3D"009229ee64e0">The solution deploys <strong>infrastructure se=
rvices rather than application builds</strong>.</p>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"5d638dccafc0" id=3D"Task13-TechnicalDocument-6.Monitoringan=
dIncidentManagement">6. Monitoring and Incident Management</h1>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"c95e5c6ae389" id=3D"Task13-TechnicalDocument-6.1MonitoringT=
oolsandMetrics">6.1 Monitoring Tools and Metrics</h1>
<p local-id=3D"a4f8ebe2c66a">The monitoring system uses:</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"8d225f26-8ab1-4d0e-a5d2-7a9=
ffc3e6b9a" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"af39bd6512cd">Tool</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"f14b04540391">Monitoring Function</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"459d8dfea1d1">Prometheus</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"be19cac4c83d">Collect infrastructure metrics</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"864aea5c4ced">Loki</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"93d065b2c8f2">Store and query logs</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"428de97a12e5">Grafana</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6b765d24dd5d">Display dashboards</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"4b639146f941">Mimir</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7a81b8ae28f9">Store metrics long-term</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"96620354705e">Key metrics include:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"61c83477b186">service availability</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"24e01b74f352">scrape performance</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"a9450f83c685">log ingestion</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"4c57e8b5a47a" id=3D"Task13-TechnicalDocument-6.2Alertingand=
Notification">6.2 Alerting and Notification</h1>
<p local-id=3D"ab37b5e12058">Alerting systems were <strong>not implemented =
in this assignment</strong>.</p>
<p local-id=3D"ec2d3703d606">Future improvements could include:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"f00360b36d36">Prometheus Alertmanager</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"88ec4f81b5ea">Grafana alerting</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"783838a62f76">Slack or email notifications</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"0869294ab2b4" id=3D"Task13-TechnicalDocument-6.3IncidentMan=
agement">6.3 Incident Management</h1>
<p local-id=3D"233c6bcb19be">Formal incident management processes are <stro=
ng>not implemented</strong>.</p>
<p local-id=3D"a53d3db7ac32">Typical incident management process would incl=
ude:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p local-id=3D"9d495e116986">alert detection</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"b2b95746ca4e">investigation</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"c7227afe355d">root cause analysis</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"895380cabd42">remediation</p></li>
</ol>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"61967e78db2d" id=3D"Task13-TechnicalDocument-7.Security&amp=
;Compliance">7. Security &amp; Compliance</h1>
<p local-id=3D"a7268bb0ec16">Security best practices implemented:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"d12d9becd4e7">service isolation using dedicated users</p></l=
i>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"b025a57611aa">restricted network ports</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"168b033bd48c">minimal system permissions</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"69207a211dd1">Future improvements could include:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"00d40bf3427d">IAM integration</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"157a2c85f542">HTTPS encryption</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"e300cabe2970">authentication controls</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"146cc2fb6f4c" id=3D"Task13-TechnicalDocument-8.CostOptimisa=
tion">8. Cost Optimisation</h1>
<p local-id=3D"5f92f659e003">The solution minimizes cost through:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"60a382639f42">open-source monitoring tools</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"2b71f6598c3b">single EC2 instance deployment</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"938675d51b32">minimal infrastructure resources</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"f15e017ace81">Cost model considerations include:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"23cab3f9e676">EC2 compute cost</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"21b6cf3c1592">storage usage</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"d8456ae0b64e">data transfer</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"cd8bb1b51e35">Business value:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"0a59073e23c4">improved operational visibility</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"b15f741604ce">faster troubleshooting</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"75868de15dbb">automated monitoring deployment</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
