<h1 local-id=3D"401338a7b3f6" id=3D"Task13-TechnicalDocument-12.Conclusion"=
>12. Conclusion</h1>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"9a9ddaccc1ec" id=3D"Task13-TechnicalDocument-12.1Summary">1=
2.1 Summary</h1>
<p local-id=3D"97970708de2d">This project demonstrates the automated deploy=
ment of an observability stack on AWS EC2 using shell scripting.</p>
<p local-id=3D"b937e12e9e21">The monitoring stack enables:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"dea08b70de1d">metrics collection</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"2255747918bb">log aggregation</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"51c8f0282738">system visibility</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"09d22ec88fdb">The solution illustrates key DevOps practices =
such as <strong>automation, monitoring, and infrastructure consistency</str=
ong>.</p>
<hr>
